sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant HK as HotkeyManager
    participant APP as TalkFlowApp
    participant AR as AudioRecorder
    participant WT as Worker Thread
    participant WE as WhisperEngine
    participant TI as TextInserter
    participant MB as MenuBarApp
    participant HS as TranscriptionHistory
    participant FS as FileSystem

    Note over APP,WE: Startup — preload_model runs in background
    APP->>WE: load_model (daemon thread)
    WE-->>WE: WhisperModel loaded

    U->>HK: Press Ctrl+.
    HK->>HK: _on_press → normalize key → add to _current_keys
    HK->>HK: _check_hotkey_match → True
    HK->>HK: _hotkey_active = True
    HK->>APP: spawn thread → on_hotkey_press

    APP->>APP: check _is_processing (False) + is_active (False)
    APP->>AR: start_recording()
    AR->>AR: _starting = True, clear chunks
    AR->>AR: sd.InputStream open + start
    AR->>AR: _recording = True, _starting = False
    AR->>AR: threading.Timer(300s) start
    AR->>APP: on_recording_start callback
    APP->>MB: set_recording_state(True)
    MB-->>MB: 🔴 icon
    APP->>APP: afplay Tink.aiff (subprocess)

    loop Audio Capture (Audio Thread)
        AR->>AR: _audio_callback(chunk)
        AR->>AR: append chunk, calc RMS
    end

    U->>HK: Release Ctrl+.
    HK->>HK: _on_release → discard from _current_keys
    HK->>HK: _hotkey_active=True AND push_to_talk mode
    HK->>HK: _check_hotkey_match → False
    HK->>HK: _hotkey_active = False
    HK->>APP: spawn thread → on_hotkey_release

    APP->>APP: poll is_recording (up to 500ms) → True
    APP->>APP: _stop_and_transcribe()
    APP->>AR: stop_recording()
    AR->>AR: cancel max_duration Timer
    AR->>AR: _recording = False
    AR->>AR: stream.stop() + stream.close()
    AR->>AR: np.concatenate chunks
    AR->>AR: check duration ≥ 0.3s ✓
    AR->>AR: check avg_rms (warn if < 0.005)
    AR->>AR: float32 → int16 conversion
    AR->>FS: write_wav /tmp/talkflow_XXXXX.wav
    AR->>APP: on_recording_stop(audio_path)
    APP->>MB: set_recording_state(False)
    APP->>APP: afplay Pop.aiff
    AR-->>APP: return /tmp/talkflow_XXXXX.wav

    APP->>WT: spawn daemon thread → _transcribe_and_insert
    WT->>WT: _is_processing = True
    WT->>MB: set_processing_state(True)
    MB-->>MB: ⏳ icon

    WT->>WE: transcribe(audio_path)
    WE->>WE: ThreadPoolExecutor(1) submit _transcribe_impl
    WE->>WE: _get_audio_duration → N.Ns
    WE->>WE: duration > 30s? → use_vad decision
    WE->>WE: model.transcribe(audio_path, kwargs...)
    WE->>WE: iterate segments, join text
    WE-->>WT: TranscriptionResult(text, language, duration)

    alt Has transcribed text
        WT->>WT: text.strip() + optional trailing space
        WT->>HS: history.add(text, language, duration, model)
        HS->>FS: save history.json (max 50 entries)
        WT->>WT: time.sleep(0.1) — cursor focus settle
        WT->>TI: insert_text(text)
        TI->>TI: pyperclip.paste() → save old_clipboard
        TI->>TI: pyperclip.copy(text)
        TI->>TI: time.sleep(0.05)
        TI->>U: keyboard.pressed(Cmd) + press/release v → Cmd+V
        TI->>TI: time.sleep(0.35) — wait rich editors
        TI->>TI: pyperclip.copy(old_clipboard) — restore
        TI-->>WT: True (success)
        WT->>APP: afplay Glass.aiff
    else No speech detected
        WT->>MB: show_notification("No speech detected")
    else Exception or Timeout
        WT->>APP: afplay Basso.aiff
        WT->>MB: show_error(str(e))
    end

    WT->>WT: _is_processing = False
    WT->>MB: set_processing_state(False)
    MB-->>MB: 🎤 icon (idle)
    WT->>FS: os.unlink /tmp/talkflow_XXXXX.wav